PLACEHOLDER — not a real keystore. Generate one with:
  keytool -genkeypair -v \
    -keystore release-learnlauncher.keystore \
    -alias learnlauncher_release \
    -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000 \
    -storepass "$ANDROID_RELEASE_STORE_PASSWORD" \
    -keypass  "$ANDROID_RELEASE_KEY_PASSWORD" \
    -dname "CN=learnlauncher-release"
See .env.template at repo root for the required env vars.
